beer.beer_description:

While spontaneity can be fun, sometimes you want to make sure your adventure will rock. Checkout the menu at an Untappd Verified Venue before visiting and know exactly whatâ€™s on tap! That's 135 check-ins at venue that is verified. Try 5 more for Level 28!
